name: Oshaberi Usagi: Mecha Kawa Oshare Collection
name_original: Oshaberi Usagi: Mecha Kawa Oshare Collection
description:
Oshaberi Usagi: Mecha Kawa Oshare Collection is a game developed by Culture Brain. It came out on 19-12-2013. It was published by CULTURE BRAIN.
Oshaberi Usagi: Mecha Kawa Oshare Collection is available on Nintendo 3DS.
